d.avif?t=1740005200 width=800 height=532 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GB VERSION</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230540/extras/64f1856ff1a855faf23a61e8c7b513b5.avif?t=1740005200\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230540/extras_big/64f1856ff1a855faf23a61e8c7b513b5.avif?t=1740005200 width=800 height=716 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All retro editions will have physical editions! Follow me on <u>KICKSTARTER</u> so you don't miss the launch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230540/extras/5ffc4620fcbabfd210717f0bb931a77b.avif?t=1740005200\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230540/extras_big/5ffc4620fcbabfd210717f0bb931a77b.avif?t=1740005200 width=800 height=490 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NES AND PC BIG BOX, GB, GBA AND SNES VERSIONS ALSO AVAILABLE!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230540/extras/da1313300b1b7fab4a7a57158ca22433.avif?t=1740005200\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230540/extras_big/da1313300b1b7fab4a7a57158ca22433.avif?t=1740005200 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cronela´s Mansion awaits you more manic than ever!</p>",
